## BugBot Integration

Cursor's BugBot generates PR summaries and flags tech debt automatically.

```
Enable: Cursor Dashboard → Settings → BugBot → Enable for repository

BugBot does automatically:
  - Summarizes changes in each PR (saves reading diff manually)
  - Flags: TODO comments, console.log, hard-coded values, security patterns
  - Tags: breaking changes, performance concerns, new dependencies

Complement with /review-diff:
  BugBot catches surface-level issues automatically
  /review-diff catches Rocket-specific issues (getSession, RLS, Stripe patterns)
  Run both before merging any PR
```

